1
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:06,120
Mimi.

2
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,330
Where did you go?

3
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,520
Mimi.

4
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:15,840
Sister, pitying yourself under the moon again?

5
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:20,080
Right, today is the day Bai Manchuan gets married.

6
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,460
Sister, does this look familiar?

7
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:27,720
What are your gloves made of?

8
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,320
You saw it all, didn't you?

9
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,000
You killed Mimi.

10
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,620
Any beast that offends me,

11
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,920
I kill as I please.

12
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,160
You killed Mimi!

13
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,840
You madwoman, give it back!

14
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,920
I already gave it back to you.

15
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,530
What are you saying?

16
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:51,240
Don't you think the soup served this afternoon

17
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:53,180
tasted particularly delicious?

18
00:01:56,160 --> 00:01:57,400
You lunatic.

19
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,800
It's not like you met me yesterday.

20
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,600
Why so agitated?

21
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,600
Qiangwei, what are you chatting about here?

22
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,600
Shen Lingbo is crazy.

23
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,720
She killed Mimi.

24
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:14,330
Kick her out of the Prime Minister's Manor immediately!

25
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,720
Qiangwei.

26
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,320
Lingbo is your sister.

27
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:20,120
I only have you two daughters.

28
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:22,920
In the future, you must support each other.

29
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,760
I have no such sister.

30
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,160
Qiangwei.

31
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,060
Father, if you feel sorry for her,

32
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:34,440
go after her.

33
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,400
Lingbo.

34
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,400
I have always treated you two

35
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:50,200
equally.

36
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:53,200
I have never favored either side.

37
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,440
What? You don't believe me?

38
00:02:56,880 --> 00:03:00,680
I heard you went to the Marquis of Loyalty and Justice's Manor today.

39
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:04,280
That Bai boy is always arrogant.

40
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,280
I wanted to goad him into defying the decree.

41
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:09,240
Pity. He didn't take the bait.

42
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:11,240
Defying a decree means losing one's head.

43
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:14,760
You don't have feelings for that Bai Manchuan, do you?

44
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,040
Don't forget.

45
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,240
You are Shen Zhao's daughter.

46
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:22,620
You cannot have any ties with the Marquis of Loyalty and Justice's Manor.

47
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:25,840
The Yueshi Kingdom delegation will arrive in the capital soon.

48
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:28,079
To escort Princess Toya for the marriage alliance.

49
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:29,840
Father, speak your mind.

50
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,400
The Emperor is ill.

51
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,920
The position of Empress is vacant.

52
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:37,640
Are you willing to vie for it for the Shen family?

53
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,920
It seems you already have a plan.

54
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:46,640
Father.

55
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,600
You will regret saying this to me.

56
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,440
Your Highness.

57
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,600
Let me ask you.

58
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,160
The girl prophesied to become the Queen of the Grassland,

59
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,200
have you found her?

60
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,160
Not yet.

61
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:06,280
What about the Marquis of Loyalty and Justice and his son?

62
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,240
Any news?

63
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,640
As you instructed,

64
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,920
I'm keeping a close watch on the Marquis's Manor

65
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:11,560
and his son, Bai Manchuan.

66
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:12,840
But,

67
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:16,640
this Bai Manchuan doesn't seem to be the one in the prophecy.

68
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:18,480
He has some skills,

69
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:19,720
but not much.

70
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,440
And he is overly compassionate.

71
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:26,960
Ruyu, have you forgotten the first lesson I taught you?

72
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:30,680
Never underestimate your enemy.

73
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,000
Since the prophecy says

74
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,520
he is close to the new Queen of the Grassland,

75
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:39,159
we can find her by watching him.

76
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,159
Father, I want a divorce.

77
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:48,400
I can't go on like this.

78
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,480
Huanghuacai is simply inhuman!

79
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:55,240
Manchuan, why can't you just live your life in peace?

80
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,000
What are you making a fuss about?

81
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,640
She forced me to read all night.

82
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:01,640
She even pricked my butt with an awl.

83
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,720
Brother, what are you wailing about?

84
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,130
You screamed all night.

85
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,880
I didn't get to sleep until dawn.

86
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:12,000
What is going on in your head?

87
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:15,800
Father, have pity on your delicate... oh, no,

88
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,320
your tough son.

89
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,200
If this goes on,

90
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,800
your son will be tortured to death.

91
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,240
Manchuan.

92
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,240
Think about it.

93
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:26,120
Look at our Bai Manor, everyone from top to bottom,

94
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:29,800
aren't we all living off your wife's dowry?

95
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,000
Do you have the heart to let them end up on the streets?

96
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:35,560
Besides, it's only her first day here,

97
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,760
and she already paid off all your debts.

98
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:40,880
Where can you find such a devoted and good girl

99
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:42,560
these days?

100
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,320
A wife paying her husband's debts

101
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,720
is perfectly justified.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:50,640
Brother, I didn't realize you were a kept man.

103
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,600
Calm down.

104
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,600
Okay?

105
00:05:59,040 --> 00:05:59,480
Miss.

106
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:01,640
Father, I, Song Xuan, offer you tea.

107
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,120
Good child. Good child.

108
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,640
My husband is making a racket outside.

109
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,170
Is he dissatisfied with me?

110
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,280
No.

111
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:13,640
He's just exercising his voice.

112
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,920
Oh.

113
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,120
In that case,

114
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,840
since you are now our Miss's husband,

115
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,440
you must observe Male Virtue at all times.

116
00:06:23,440 --> 00:06:24,280
Male Virtue?

117
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,120
What is Male Virtue?

118
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,160
Never heard of it.

119
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,280
You've heard of it now, Husband.

120
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:32,159
What if I don't comply?

121
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,730
The Daylily is murdering her husband!

122
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,560
Aim better! Don't hit me!

123
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,570
If you keep this up, I'll sleep in a separate room.

124
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:04,200
When I got there, it was too late.

125
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:07,200
This was all I could do.

126
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,680
Thank you, Marquis, for traveling so far

127
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,840
and disobeying military orders

128
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,880
to retrieve the remains of the Song Army.

129
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,000
This kindness,

130
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,760
I will remember forever.

131
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,880
You give me too much credit.

132
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:19,640
Father.

133
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,520
Brother.

134
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:22,000
Rest assured.

135
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:25,530
I will protect everything of the Song family for you.

136
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:33,240
Miss.

137
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:36,120
There is something off about the accounts of Marquis Zhongyi's Manor.

138
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,080
What's wrong?

139
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,240
I checked.

140
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:42,000
The missing amount is exactly the 500,000 taels of the Song Army's pay.

141
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,460
Check it again carefully.

142
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,320
Young Master! Young Master!

143
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,800
Young Master, I checked.

144
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,200
The Young Madam is not in the manor.

145
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,730
Her maid isn't here either.

146
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:13,200
Xuelan, Xuelan.

147
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,160
If you have something important, say it quickly.

148
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,280
That Daylily at home is terrifying.

149
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:20,080
If she finds out, I'll get a thrashing.

150
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,720
Xuelan.

151
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,960
Xuelan.

152
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:59,060
Xuelan has something important to discuss with me.

153
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,170
I'm the one looking for you.

154
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,820
Why are you dressed like that?

155
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,040
Do you like it?

156
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,320
Lingbo.

157
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:17,080
You must have heard.

158
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,880
I'm married.

159
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:22,280
Are you willing to live with such a cruel woman

160
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:23,400
for the rest of your life?

161
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,880
The Emperor decreed it. I can't divorce her.

162
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:31,320
Then at least stay the night.

163
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,080
Father,

164
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,120
Brother,

165
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:37,200
please watch over me,

166
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,780
help me find the truth soon

167
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,840
and avenge you.

168
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,400
Miss.

169
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:43,880
Miss.

170
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:46,800
Bad news. Young Master Bai went to Baihua Tower again.

171
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:47,200
Man...

172
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,080
Miss.

173
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,040
This won't do.

174
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,610
This is Baihua Tower, the best in Dasheng.

175
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:02,680
Bring out all the girls for me to see.

176
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,120
Sir,

177
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,520
sorry, we're fully booked today.

178
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,520
We're closed.

179
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:11,160
Are you rejecting me?

180
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:13,680
No.

181
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,040
I have plenty of beauties here.

182
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:17,100
Wait a moment, I'll call them for you.

183
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,000
No need.

184
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,480
This one looks fine to me.

185
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,120
I didn't expect such a beauty in Dasheng.

186
00:10:27,520 --> 00:10:28,680
What's your name?

187
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,480
Who are you? Hands off!

188
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:37,920
Get away!

189
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,800
Man Chuan!

190
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:44,160
What's your name?

191
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,200
Shen Lingbo.

192
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:50,920
Lingbo. It suits you.

193
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,480
I've decided.

194
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:54,160
You'll be my woman.

195
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:56,440
Come. Drink with me.

196
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,080
Bring the best wine and food.

197
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,120
Hurry!

198
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:07,960
Let her go.
